# A small OOP project Library Management System

My program consists
1. a librarian and
2. a member
basing on them the activities are designed
1. Add Book
2. View All Books
3. Search Book
4. Register Member
5. View Members
6. Borrow Book
7. Return Book
8. Delete Book
9. Save Data
10. Exit


Exceptions:

TypeError         - Wrong data type used in an operation
ValueError        - Correct type, but invalid value (e.g., `int("abc")`)
NameError         - Variable not defined
IndexError        - List index out of range
KeyError          - Dictionary key not found
ZeroDivisionError - Division by zero
FileNotFoundError - File doesn't exist
AttributeError    - Object doesn't have the requested attribute
